# App Restart Workflow

- After any code change in this repo, restart the running AnimalTracker app before reporting completion.
- Check existing terminals or processes first and avoid spawning duplicate app instances.
- Stop the current AnimalTracker app process and start a single fresh instance.
- Leave unrelated watchers alone unless they also need a restart.
- Wait long enough to confirm the app restarted successfully before reporting completion.
- If restarting would be unsafe or ambiguous, ask before proceeding.
